â˜ï¸  MODULE 1 â€” Onboarding & Cloud SetupConnect your existing infrastructure in minutes. No DevOps knowledge needed.

The first thing a new client does after signing up is complete a guided onboarding flow. This connects their existing cloud accounts, code repositories, and business tools to the platform so everything is accessible from one place.

Feature | Description
Guided Onboarding Wizard | Step-by-step setup assistant walks the client through connecting all their accounts. Each step is explained in plain language with visual cues.
GCP Integration | Connect Google Cloud Platform projects. The platform can read, deploy, and manage cloud resources (Cloud Run, Cloud Storage, Firebase) on behalf of the client.
AWS Integration | Connect Amazon Web Services accounts via IAM role. Supports EC2, S3, Lambda, and RDS. Future-proof for clients already using AWS infrastructure.
GitHub Repository Sync | Connect one or more GitHub repositories. The platform reads existing code and uses it as the base when clients request new features or improvements via prompts.
